
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>StartupDna</title>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
<%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="border-top"></div>
  <div class="content">

    <div class="first-line">
      <h1 class="logo-text"><a>smashbot</a></h1>
        <ul class="blog-tags">
          <li><h5><a>apprentice.io</a></h5></li>
          <li><h5><a>design</a></h5></li>
          <li><h5><a>checklist</a></h5></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="second-line">
      <div class="logo-background">
      <%= image_tag "smashbot-logo.png", :class => "logo-icon" %>
      </div>
      <h2 class="title">How to become a design apprentice</h2>
      <h3 class="subtitle">Checklist for future apprentices</h3>
      <h6 class="blogger-name"><a>ed wassermann</a></h6>
    </div>
    
    <div class="third-line">
      <h5 class="date">06/10/2013</h5>
      <p class="blog-text"><span class="capital_letter">A</span>pplying for the <span class="italics"><a>design apprenticeship</a></span> was certainly the best decision for becoming a better craftsman. The high value <span class="italics">smashbot</span> puts into learning and educating each other creates an excellent environment for expanding your
      knowledge and to professionalize your skills. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="homer-background">
      <%= image_tag "Homer-complex-car.jpg", :class => "homer-icon" %>
    </div>

    <div class="fourth-block">
      
      <ul>

      <div class="wrapper"> 
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">1</span>irst</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Hop on the <strong><a>trail map</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">2</span>econd</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Get dangerous at <strong><a>typography</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">3</span>hird</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Catch yourself ranting about bad typefaces in a restaurant</li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">4</span>ourth</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Know thy <strong><a>grids</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">5</span>ifth</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Know thy <strong><a>color wheel</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">6</span>ixth</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Annoy friends and family with <strong><a>design principles</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">7</span>eventh</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Start using <strong><a>Bourbon<a/> & <a>Neat</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">8</span>igth</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Get offended by unsemantic <strong><a>HTML</a> / <a>CSS</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">9</span>inth</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Design a <strong><a>pet project</a> </strong>and ask for feedback</li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">10</span>enth</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Get more access to the <strong><a>Team</a></strong> through <strong><a>PRIME</a></strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">11</span>leventh</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %>Do the online / offline <strong><a>“Design for Developers”</a> </strong>workshop</li>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="check-ordinals">
          <li class="ordinals"><span class="ordinal-letter">12</span>welfth</li>
        </div>
        <div class="check-lines">
          <li class="list"><%= image_tag "red-line.jpg", :class => "red-line" %><strong>Enjoy the process!</strong></li>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      </ul>
    </div>

      <%= yield %>

    </div>
    <div class="border-bottom">
      <div class="copyright"><p>© 2013 smashbot, inc. The design of a robot and smashbot are registered trademarks of smashbot, inc.</p> 
      </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
